cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.PL

Reasoning: 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on developing and testing AI agents for a game.
- cs.GT (Game Theory) is also likely as the paper discusses a game and its rules, and how to optimise agents to play it.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses evolutionary algorithms and optimisers to tune the AI agents.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with optimising a system (the AI agent) to perform well in a game.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also less likely but possible as the paper may discuss the programming language used to implement the game and the AI agents.
